{"word":"φυλή","slug":"φυλή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>φυλή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φύω\">φύω</a></el> ‘put forth, produce’] ‘people subgroup’, as qualified in context<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in general, of earth’s people subgroups or people-groups <b>people, people group <a href='B:730 13:7'>Rv 13:7</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> <b>peoples <a href='B:470 24:30'>Mt 24:30</a>; <a href='B:730 1:7'>Rv 1:7</a>; <a href='B:730 7:9'>7:9</a>; <a href='B:730 11:9'>11:9</a>; <a href='B:730 14:6'>14:6</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of Israelite ancestral blood-lines <b>tribe <a href='B:470 19:28'>Mt 19:28</a>; <a href='B:490 22:30'>Lk 22:30</a>; <a href='B:650 7:13'>Hb 7:13f</a>; <a href='B:660 1:1'>Js 1:1</a>;</b> with specific name cited <b><a href='B:490 2:36'>Lk 2:36</a>; <a href='B:510 13:21'>Ac 13:21</a>; <a href='B:520 11:1'>Ro 11:1</a>; <a href='B:570 3:5'>Phil 3:5</a>; <a href='B:730 5:5'>Rv 5:5</a>; <a href='B:730 7:4'>7:4</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ch.\">ch.</a> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:φυλάσσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:φύλλον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}